        ## Tutorial
        ### Start project
        TBD
        
        ### Models
        
        ```python
        from brink import models
        
        
        class Message(models.Model):
        
            schema = {
                "message": {"type": "string"},
                "sender": {"type": "string"}
            }
        ```
        
        ### Handlers
        
        ```python
        async def handle_honks(request, ws):
            async for honk in Honk.changes().all():
                ws.send_json(honk)
        ```
        
